Class CamelTemplate

java.lang.Object
cz.radeknolc.cameljourney.CamelTemplate
public class CamelTemplate extends Object
Camel Template is class that handles information about possible camels that can be generated.

  • Constructor Details

    • CamelTemplate

      public CamelTemplate(String templateName, double speedMin, double speedMax, double distanceMin, double distanceMax, double drinkTime, int maxLoad, double ratio)
      Constructor of Camel Template
      Parameters:
      templateName - name of the camel template
      speedMin - minimum speed for calculation that can camel have
      speedMax - maximum speed for calculation that can camel have
      distanceMin - minimum distance for calculation that can camel travel
      distanceMax - maximum distance for calculation that can camel travel
      drinkTime - how much time it takes to drink
      maxLoad - how many stretchers are possible to load
      ratio - generation probability from 0.00 to 1.00, 1.00 equals to 100 %
